response.original_title: Phoebe Robinson: I Don't Wanna Work Anymore
response.overview: In Phoebe's sophomore stand-up special, she's bringing her raw and unfiltered perspective to the myths of being a girlboss, the fresh hell of wearing a thong, and the real reason women start book clubs and launch Etsy businesses.
response.title: Phoebe Robinson: I Don't Wanna Work Anymore
